    "safetyTipsTitle": "Talooyin Amaan",
    "safetyTipsDesc": "Sida aaminsan loo ganacsado baaro",
    "readGuide": "Hagaha Akhriso",
    "heroTitle": "Sidee kuu caawin karnaa?",
    "heroSubtitle": "Jawaabaha su'aalaha caadiga ah ee ku saabsan iibsashada, iibinta, iyo ammaanka Suqafuran ka hel.",
    "faqBuy1Q": "Sideen ku iibsanayaa shay Suqafuran?",
    "faqBuy1A": "Iibsashadu waa fudud! Xayeysiisyada baadh ama raadi, guji mid aad jeceshahay, oo isticmaal badhanka \"Sheeko\" ama \"Lambarka Muuji\" si aad gadeeyaha toos ula xiriirto. Mar walba meel caafimaad leh oo dadweyne ah ku kulmow si aad shayga u hubeysid ka hor intaadan bixin.",
    "faqBuy2Q": "Qiimayaashu miyay la xaajoodsanayaan?",
    "faqBuy2A": "Gadaayaasha badankood waxay u furan yihiin qiimeyaasha. Qiimaha waxaad kala hadli kartaa gadeeyaha iyada oo loo marayo sheekada barnaamijka gudihiisa ama adigoo u wacaya. Raadso calaamada \"La Xaajoodsanayaa\" ee xayeysiisyada.",
    "faqSell1Q": "Sideen u geliyaa xayeysiis?",
    "faqSell1A": "Dhagsii badhanka \"Xayeysiis Cusub Geli\" ee xaafaddaada ama badhanka \"Hadda Iib\" ee madaxa. Qaybta dooro, sawiro cad soo geli, cinwaan iyo qiime sharraxaad leh ku dar, ka dibna guji \"Xayeysiiska Geli\". Bilaash buu yahay!",
    "faqSell2Q": "Sideen u iibiyaa alaabadayda dhakhso?",
    "faqSell2A": "Si dhakhso ah u iibiso: 1. Sawiro tayo sare leh isticmaal. 2. Sharaxaad faahfaahsan qor. 3. Qiime xaq ah oo tartamaya ku dhig. 4. Noqo \"Gadeeyaha La Xaqiijiyay\" si aad kalsoonida dheeri ah musharriyayaasha ula dhisid.",
    "faqSafety1Q": "Sideen u aaminsan u gabacsadaa?",
    "faqSafety1A": "Ammaanku waa mudnaanteena. Mar walba meelaha dadweyne (sida xarumaha ganacsi ama kafeeha) ku kulmow, lacag ha u dirin ka hor intaadan shayga arkayn, oo kalsooni nafsiga u qaado. Haddii heshiis aad ujeedo wanaagsan u leeyahay, waxaa laga yaabaa inay run tahay.",
    "faqSafety2Q": "Barnaamijka Gadeeyaha La Xaqiijiyay waa maxay?",
    "faqSafety2A": "Barnaamijkeena Gadeeyaha La Xaqiijiyay wuxuu astaan u siiyaa gadaayaasha warqadda aqoonsiga rasmiga ah soo gudbiyay. Tani waxay musharriyayaasha ka caawisaa inay xulafada la aaminsan yihiin. Xaqiijinta waad codsan kartaa goobaha akoonkaaga.",
    "faqAccount1Q": "Sideen u bedelaa eraygayga sirta?",
    "faqAccount1A": "Tag \"Goobaha Akoonka\" ee barra dhinaca xaafaddaada. Qaybta \"Amniga\", waxaad cusbooneysiin kartaa eraygaaga sirta oo maamusho xidhmadaada firfircoon.",
    "faqAccount2Q": "Eraygayga sirta waan ilowday, maxaan sameeyaa?",
    "faqAccount2A": "Bogga galitaanka, guji \"Eraygii Sirta Ilowday?\". Ciwaankaaga iimeelka geli, oo xiriir ammaan ah ayaan kuu diri doonnaa si aad dib u dejiso."
